Invocation Name: workout coach
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Workout Guide is a Fitness and Health skill to help health-conscious individuals attain their health-focused lifestyles and fitness goals.
Use the guide to find a suitable exercise for any muscle group, equipment or level. You can even search for a combination of these.
The guide can describe how to perform a particular exercise. It comes with a daily workout, and you can set a daily reminder.
